  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Each base of a right rectangular prism has a length of <math alttext=\"19\"><mn>19</mn>\n</math> inches and a width of <math alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn>\n</math> inches. The prism has a volume of <math alttext=\"2,736\"><mn>2,736</mn>\n</math> cubic inches. What is the height, in inches, of the prism?</p>",
