ext=\"2,736 equals left parenthesis 19 right parenthesis left parenthesis 8 right parenthesis left parenthesis h right parenthesis\"><mn>2,736</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>19</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>)</mo></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"2,736 equals 152 h\"><mn>2,736</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>152</mn><mi>h</mi></math>. Dividing each side of this equation by <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"152\"><mn>152</mn></math> yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"18 equals h\"><mn>18</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>h</mi></math>. Therefore, the height, in inches, of the prism is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"18\"><mn>18</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect. This is the area, in square inches, of the base of the prism, not the height, in inches, of the prism.</p>",
